# Strategi Master Data — Dummy App vs ERP Terpisah

| Tanggal | 5 Juni 2026 |

---

## 1. Kondisi saat ini

```mermaid
flowchart TB
  subgraph app [BOM Design Baru - TODAY]
    SEED[src/data/masters/*.json]
    IDB[(IndexedDB browser)]
    IMP[npm run import:masters:zan]
    SEED --> IDB
    IMP --> SEED
  end
  subgraph erp [ERPKu Staging - TARGET]
    DB[(PostgreSQL / ERP DB)]
    API_M[/purchasing/materials]
    API_WC[/manufacture/work-centers]
    API_R[/manufacture/routings]
    DB --> API_M
    DB --> API_WC
    DB --> API_R
  end
  PICKER[Material Picker] --> IDB
  PICKER -. future .-> API_M
```

| Aspek | App (dummy) | ERP (live) |
|-------|-------------|------------|
| Lokasi | File JSON + browser | Database server |
| Update | Reset import / patch seed | Admin ERP UI |
| Scope | ~882 SKU ZAN seed | Semua material pabrik |
| COATING/RATIO/FORMULA | Ada di seed | ❌ tidak exposed di BOM UI |
| FOB COST | Seed Excel | ❌ |
| Work Center | Seed | `/manufacture/work-centers` |
| Routing template | Seed + node-level | `/manufacture/routings` |

**Poin user (req #6):** Master di app saat ini **dummy sementara**; nantinya **dipisah** mengikuti pola **erp.solusiuntuknegeri** (modul master terpisah, BOM hanya konsumen).

---

## 2. Target arsitektur master

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  Admin[Master Admin ERP] --> MDB[(Master DB)]
  MDB --> API[Master API Layer]
  API --> BOM_APP[BOM Costing App]
  API --> WC_UI[Work Centers UI]
  API --> MAT_UI[Materials UI]
  EXCEL[Excel Import Batch] --> MDB
```

### Prinsip pemisahan

1. **Single source of truth** = ERP master modules
2. **BOM app read-only** master (kecuali admin role)
3. **Cache lokal** optional untuk offline dev only (`MASTER_SOURCE=seed`)
4. **Formula/ratio/coating** — expose via API atau sub-module `manufacture/costing-master`

