## 4. Fase transisi

| Fase | Mode | `MASTER_SOURCE` | User impact |
|------|------|-----------------|-------------|
| **T0** (now) | Seed JSON | `seed` | Dev/demo; dummy prices |
| **T1** | Hybrid | `hybrid` | Kayu/hardware ERP; ratio seed |
| **T2** | ERP primary | `erp` | All pickers API |
| **T3** | ERP only | `erp` (seed deprecated) | Production |

### Acceptance per fase

**T1 Hybrid:**
- [ ] Picker kayu + hardware dari API
- [ ] Fallback seed jika API down (banner warning)

**T2 ERP primary:**
- [ ] Reset import disabled in production build
- [ ] WC + routing from API
- [ ] Audit `npm run audit:database` hits ERP endpoint

